## Why This Is Asked

Tests the ability to design a scalable, governed, multi-region data lake with reliable ingestion, deduplication, and schema evolution.

## Key Concepts

- Regional ingestion paths and Parquet data lake
- Lake Formation governance and CRR
- Idempotent ingestion with event_id dedup
- Schema evolution via Avro + Glue Schema Registry
- Late data handling and e2e testing

## Code Example

```javascript
// Pseudocode dedupe
async function isDuplicate(event_id){
  const exists = await dynamo.get({PK: event_id});
  if (exists) return true;
  await dynamo.put({PK: event_id, ...});
  return false;
}
```

